edu.iu.dsc.tws.api.tset.sets

Interface StorableTBase<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, TBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CachedTSet, CheckpointedTSet, KeyedCachedTSet, KeyedCheckpointedTSet, KeyedPersistedTSet, KeyedStoredTSet, PersistedTSet, StoredTSet

    public interface StorableTBase<T>
extends TBase, java.io.Serializable
    All TSets that store data would need to implement this interface. This defines the methods that other classes can use to access the stored data. Once the data is stored, it would be exposed to as another "SourceTSet".
